#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:627
msgid ""
"calibre can automatically convert ``.docx`` files created by Microsoft Word "
"2007 and newer. Just add the file to calibre and click convert (make sure "
"you are running the latest version of calibre as support for ``.docx`` files"
